ent of your life on earth.', 2878, 0), (173183, 'The city was alive, and so was he...', 25140, 0), (173184, 'Do not fall in love.....it means you have to look at someone else.', 3698, 0), (173185, 'There are a thousand reasons to live this life, every one of them sufficient.', 1383, 0), (173186, 'Work passionately.', 2878, 0), (173187, 'Even a lion finds time to relax and look for a good spot.', 5405, 0), (173188, 'Success, It makes you beautiful', 22629, 0), (173189, 'To live without zest is to live without an appetite for new experiences, to miss out on the spice, the juice, the edge that makes life thrilling. It is to live with deadened, flattened senses, with your passions unaroused and your curiosity untapped.', 32004, 0), (173190, 'When I have opportunity to walk, I never miss it.', 2878, 0), (173191, 'I keep thinking and worry about life, he says...I asked him: can you change yesterday?he said: no..I asked him: do you know what will happen tomorrow?he said: no..If you do not know what will happen in the future?and if you can not change the past?that means you only have today.Start living Life while you have it.Today.', 31195, 0), (173192, 'You never lose anyone definitely', 32005, 0), (173193, 'Honoring your feelings awakens your soul. Feelings keep you awake. And it is from that awake place, that sound, that you build your life.', 25144, 0), (173194, 'Dancing is about enjoying life. One of the hardest things for us to do is to dance.', 25144, 0), (173195, 'Such was life that morning: nothing really mattered that much, not the good things and not the bad ones. We were in the business of mutual amusement, and we were reasonably prosperous." (pg. 18)', 9, 0), (173196, 'Love is one of life’s greatest pleasures, as it is one of life’s greatest perils.', 32006, 0), (173197, 'Being mindful of our feelings we will get Delighted. The quality of life is in proportion of our capacity to get delighted. The capacity for delight is within our capacity to pay attention to 