et away with anything. You were just born, fucked around for a while, got hit by a car and died, and that''s your whole life story right there. You don''t win by getting through all you life not having done anything.', 4764, 0), (173229, 'Life gives us experiences, we are learners.', 2878, 0), (173230, 'You see, God didn''t create us to merely survive. He created us to thrive! We were made for abundant life.', 7289, 0), (173231, 'People today are quick to bite the hand that fed them yesterday, turn around and cry hungry tomorrow.', 5815, 0), (173232, 'Always remember, difficult situations are thrust upon those who have the power to influence events.', 26532, 0), (173233, 'We can all have plenty of lives, but there are limits. You never can tell what they are.', 27793, 0), (173234, 'I keep thinking and worry about life, he says...I asked him: can you change yesterday?he said: no..I asked him: do you know what will happen tomorrow?he said: no..If you do not know what will happen tomorrowand if you can not change yesterdaythat means you only have today.Start living Life while you have it.Today.', 32014, 0), (173235, 'Life is not about in what we are living , in happy or in pain,in poor or rich,but its all about how we are living ,index of human is only honesty in character and self respect, Best Thing we can do in life its honesty,honesty with Self and with others also But we Can''t be honest with others if we are not with our self, Our Soul Leave our body when we die,but our soul meet with us when we on death bed.', 6292, 0), (173236, 'I want to be part of the happiness team - let''s create the happiness team - from love, not greed, love of life & our planet, true & free.', 3548, 0), (173237, 'Time is life.Take time to plan your life.', 2878, 0), (173238, 'Every day were reborn.', 2878, 0), (173239, 'What is life if not laughter and love, caring and compassion, fresh bread and crisp radishes?', 4074, 0), (173240, 'I look at this life as a puzzle without all the pieces