s, the yet-to-be-dismantled elms, the geese.', 8852, 0), (173429, 'Every stage of life is unique.At any age and stage of life there are obstacles and opportunities, trials and triumphs. Never allow the negative bring to you to sudden halt.Make the most of the positive opportunities and stay positive.', 2878, 0), (173430, 'The power of life and death lies in the use of the tongue. Be careful of your words.', 2878, 0), (173431, 'Most of life is just a preparation for getting ready to be dead for a very long period of time.', 344, 0), (173432, 'Life is an endless attempt to word the unwordable, to make what cannot be touched walk on the ground, to embody what can never be fit inside a single lifetime. We see reflections of ourselves in sunrises, hear our perfection in thunderstorms and babies'' laughter--touch, taste and feel--and then try to somehow remember all of that while taking out the trash, paying bills and a million other ways we have invented to forget.We weave together within ourselves mud and spirit, shadow and light, animal and angel.No wonder humans feel crazy most of the time.But you aren''t crazy. You are doing a heroic thing by being here as yourself.', 2073, 0), (173433, 'Don''t put too much trust on your education level, girlfriend, boyfriend, wife, husband, bank account, because they will fail you. Only put your 100% trust on God, you will succeed !', 11055, 0), (173434, 'Hope is not a sin, neither is fidelity.', 32036, 0), (173435, 'Hope is not a sin, and neither is fidelity.', 32036, 0), (173436, 'Time passes by, memory staysTorturing silently, rest of our days... Sigh!', 32037, 0), (173437, 'Now If diversity were inherently good, inherently valuable, inherently wonderful, why would we have to have the highly-paid profession know as ''diversity consultant'' to manage it? Things that are inherently good, to enjoy them, or to make the most of them, you don''t need a consultant. You don''t need a consultant to make the most out of good-tasting food, 